articles.title: Apple’s iPhone 17 lineup is looking a little Pixelated - The Verge
articles.description: Leaked CAD renders of what are purported to be the iPhone 17, 17 Pro, 17 Pro Max, and 17 Air — feature a Pixel-like rectangular camera bar.
articles.content:
The upcoming Pro and Air models may feature a wider, pill-shaped rear camera module similar to Googles Pixel 9.
